metadata.name: Puppet Master #1/10
metadata.description:
In the distant future, advanced mechs roam the earth. Their advanced technology and artificial intelligence allow them to perform tasks and entertain audiences in ways that were once thought impossible. Among these mechs is the puppet master, a towering machine with long, slender arms and delicate fingers that move with lightning-fast precision.

The red mech stands below, a testament to advanced engineering, its sturdy build, and its shining metallic exterior shimmering in the light. 
Despite its smaller size, the red mech exudes a sense of strength and stability, a stark contrast to the graceful movements of the puppet master. 
3600 x 3600
